{"tid":1829347,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大埔寵物店虐狗案 今次終於唔係話同勇武組織有關嗱？","createTime":"2020-01-18T16:06:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-18T16:14:38.000Z","uid":284485,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"24db182ad8818386986c6cd977e47e64f2a75a07","tid":1829347,"uid":284485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T16:06:22.000Z","msg":"乜唔係話會針對聽日嘅集會活動<br />\n作出攻擊行動咩？<br />\n有冇搵到坦克車同炭疽菌？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大埔寵物店虐狗案　警方估計至少涉七隻狗<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=377233&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D377233%26refer%3DShare&d=hCh8nFxZocjAH0BHn0nK1DQSOVv8pHkqsyXWJi2kweQ%3D&h=dcd08d0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D377233%26refer%3DShare&h=60702a8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=377233&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】大埔一間寵物美容店懷疑有人虐待狗隻，警方接到報案，把案件列作殘酷對待動物處理，拘捕一名店舖負責人。<br />\n<br />\n警方先後接獲四宗相關報案，晚上封鎖涉案店舖調查，並帶走28歲女店主，她涉嫌虐待動物。行動中撿獲藤條、狗繩及記事本等證物。<br />\n<br />\n從網上片段看到一名女子多次大力拍打一隻狗，狗隻受驚掙扎。有狗主事後向區議員求助，指狗隻完成護理服務後，眼睛、耳朵紅腫、後腳行動不便。<br />\n<br />\n警方指，連同片中的狗隻，估計案件至少涉及七隻狗，會翻查寵物美容店閉路電視片段，及呼籲懷疑寵物受虐待的客人和警方聯絡。"},{"pid":"fba91a723ef3c83dff0db086b87fb51b69b1a630","tid":1829347,"uid":274136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T16:14:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/53f4dAb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F53f4dAb.gif&h=755d7b56&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}